Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像补给延迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似前线又后退了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也不知道能坚持多久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再说这种事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让武士听到了可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 英雄 迟到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意强度计算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三号板的韧性…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 生驹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的试验怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:04:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压力应该已经足够了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能用普通的铅弹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就跟武士的蒸汽枪一样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被卡巴内的心包膜弹开的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要用喷流弹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须在贯穿力上下一番工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能代替武士去和卡巴内战斗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没疯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加炸药了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次调整的时候不是把空洞部分增大了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是这个 逞生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么就把这个步骤跳过了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 工作结束之后再…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是菖蒲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四方川家的那位？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万事都应自己亲眼确认…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是菖蒲大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么风把您吹来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是父亲的短枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太好使了 想请你帮忙看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 让您跑一趟辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是个美人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是武士家的千金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生驹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这边来帮菖蒲大人的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会来啦 英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想成为英雄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不喜欢逃避而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲大人 这把枪是要对谁使的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开西城门啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲铁城来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲铁城不是应该明天才来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是甲铁城？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可今晚扶桑城也要来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天之内居然来两辆骏城
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 甲铁城不是应该明天才来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速谷站沦陷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停靠车站少了 到站自然也就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接检查匣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有被咬到的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是正要检查吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过检查身上是否有咬痕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来判断有没有被卡巴内感染
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦发现就打入大牢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上头一贯的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一是在潜伏期呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 开始整修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有颈动脉变粗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然病毒是从这里通过的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状态如此完好的 可是少见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是违禁行为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根本就不是什么诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们不都知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁 大户人家的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那边的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出口在反方向 小孩也要接受检查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「人不可貌相 海水不可斗量」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长大人是这样告诉我的 胡子大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 这位是我的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这里的老大？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下四方川家家主 名叫坚将
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四方川大人 给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是四文大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情已从此前信中知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请先移步寒舍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用接受检查的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卡巴内
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他身上有伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡巴内
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我不是卡巴内
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不站住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围起来杀死他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊 我真的不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说他不是卡巴内了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有感染卡巴内嫌疑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要关三天来判断真伪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你们定下的规矩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还轮不到你这个蒸汽工匠多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说 你们的枪口…指错对象了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡巴内的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会拿着那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 为什么会拿着那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:10:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 他不是卡巴内啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们不觉得可耻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对什么都战战兢兢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丧失了理智
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真会说大话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身处被武士保护的安全地带
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是想怎么说都行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 即便是我也能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来栖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贯穿枪马上就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个人关进牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有感染卡巴内的嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖蒲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维护秩序也是武士的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秩序…吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTB----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 二位要去金刚郭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军大人怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还未向将军大人禀报
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次只有我们两个去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要到六月了呢 兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你 那个收集尸体的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无名？是你的名字吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼…不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兄长大人给我取的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 刚才你知道那个人不是卡巴内吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 但是总不能袖手旁观吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般都会袖手旁观吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 那个「一般」是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈 你真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有趣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一般人都会觉得卡巴内很可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就是会害怕的胆小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什么没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「因为害怕而舍弃他人 这也是没办法的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种说法 我一点都不认同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不能因为恐惧 就失去为人的品格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生驹还真是蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就冲动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副正义使者的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:14:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 顶撞武士这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算想做也做不出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这就叫蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 是扶桑城
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回倒是很准时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快减速
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况不妙 把吊桥升起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卡巴内
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卡巴内
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是警钟声！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡巴内来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用贯穿枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要用那个才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我也要带走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西门已被攻破
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再待在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.74,0:16:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去甲铁城吧 跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 您要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去甲铁城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 您要放弃这个站吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在确保甲铁城无虞之后 我会发出信号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候你也过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡巴内会对血有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下 把衣服脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑 卡巴内就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要你们证明自己身上没伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生驹人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回不会再失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸药的分量也增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我造的贯穿枪 打穿了卡巴内的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我造的！我成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了 是甲铁城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:19:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无名大人 之后请您独自前往
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请赶往金刚郭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里等候少主的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.45,0:19:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 愿你轮回来世有所福报
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要病毒还未抵达大脑 就没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年 可是过了五年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是了为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下决心与卡巴内战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…跟那个时候不一样了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…不会再逃避了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次…我一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做一个能以己为荣的人
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------OPCN----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:37.27,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}还能否记得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.89,0:21:40.67,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}在那日的蒸汽中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:48.47,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}失去了许多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:57.13,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}曾犯下的无数错误
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:22:02.60,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}看不到前路之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:05.12,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}你这样说道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.21,0:22:10.68,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}「叩问自己那涌动的血脉」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.94,0:22:13.77,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}回应那跳动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:21.69,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}前进吧 钢铁的卡巴内里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.76,0:22:28.68,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}奋勇起身 赌上自己的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.79,0:22:34.10,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}此刻 为了起誓的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.20,0:22:36.78,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}燃尽这生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:42.89,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}去改变世界
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------INEN----------------------------
