Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs46\fscx92\shad0\blur2}How much strength our bodies have achieved
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs46\fscx92\shad0\blur2}Won't you please forgive yourself ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs46\fscx92\shad0\blur2}And the tears will go above the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs46\fscx92\shad0\blur2}We had made every damn single mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(200,200)\b0\fs46\fscx92\shad0\blur2}That's what it's all about
